[[!meta title="Energy Drink — Red Bull Winter Edition Fuji Apple & Ginger Sugarfree"]]
[[!tag Energy_Drink Review]]

A recent trend for Red Bull, they've begun releasing sugarfree versions of their
seasonal Editions. Prior to 2024's
[[Red_Bull_Winter_Edition_Iced_Vanilla_Berry_Sugarfree]], Editions had no
sugarfree option. We live in the new age. An [[Energy Drink
Renaissance|Living_In_The_Energy_Drink_Renaissance]].

Overpowering taste of ginger and brightly sweetened with acesulfame potassium.
It's quite bitter. Not as easy to drink as the full-sugar Winter Edition this
year but very good nonetheless.

Considering the tradeoff in calories for only a minor change in taste this is my
go-to if I'm craving this Winter Edition.
